  "//browserslist": "Floor set to Safari/iOS 15.4 so the build transpiles away class `static {}` blocks, RegExp lookbehind, etc. — syntax that lands only in Safari 16.4+. Without this, Next 16 emits `static {}` in its core App Router chunk and iPadOS 16.2 Safari throws a parse-time SyntaxError → blank page on older iPads. David runs an iPad Pro on iPadOS 16.2. Don't raise the Safari floor above 15.4.",
  "browserslist": [
    "Chrome >= 90",
    "Firefox >= 90",
    "Edge >= 90",
    "Safari >= 15.4",
    "iOS >= 15.4"
  ]
